strings:
<voice_0x010009F0><se_high>*: Oh! Look out!
It isn't safe here!

<voice_0x010009F1><se_high>*: Just look! There's a mouse!
I hate mice! Why do I have to deal with it?
Ohhh...

<voice_0x010009F2><se_high>*: See!? See!?
Did you see it?
Just now!?

<voice_0x010009F3><se_high>*: What am I going to do!?
Jessica's room is on the other side of that wall! Oh, dear...
